INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES (2,1,1,'Open Call Narasumber Komunitas Belajar','open-call-narasumber-komunitas-belajar','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Komunitas Belajar merupakan salah satu bentuk pengembangan profesi yang bertujuan untuk memperluas pemahaman dan penerapan pendekatan dalam lingkup profesinya. Jabatan fungsional sebagai bentuk jabatan dengan dasar keahlian memerlukan wadah untuk bertukar pandangan, menyampaikan gagasan, serta mengaktualisasikan diri sebagai insan profesional.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Aspro SDMA sebagai organisasi profesi memberikan media bagi anggota untuk saling berbagi dan membangun sinergi untuk kualitas penyelenggaraan managemen SDM Aparatur yang berkualias dan profesional.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Komunitas Belajar Aspro SDMA direncanakan diselenggarakan selama </span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">1 bulan sekali /2 bulan sekali. Berkenaan dengan hal tersebut,<span style=\"color: red;\"> </span><span style=\"color: black;\">Divisi Pengembangan Insani membuka kesempatan kepada seluruh anggota Aspro SDMA untuk mengikuti <em>Open Call </em>Narasumber Komunitas Belajar dengan rincian sebagai berikut:</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">A.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Persyaratan</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 36.0pt;\"><em><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Open call</span></em><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"> Narasumber Komunitas Belajar ini ditujukan bagi anggota AsproSDMA yang menduduki Jabatan Fungsional Analis SDM Aparatur maupun Pranata SDM Aparatur dan memenuhi persyaratan administrasi sebagai berikut:</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 2.0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Melakukan Pendaftaran melalui website AsproSDMA dengan tautan sebagai berikut </span><code><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/narasumberkombelasprosdma\">https://bit.ly/narasumberkombelasprosdma</a></span></strong></span></code></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 2.0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Mengunggah Daftar riwayat hidup/CV terbaru;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 2.0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Memiliki wawasan dan pengetahuan konseptual maupun teknis tentang Manajemen SDM Aparatur dan pengalaman dalam bidang Manajemen SDM Aparatur.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 2.0cm;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0cm; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">B.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Tata Cara Pendaftaran</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l6 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 54.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Peserta melakukan pendaftaran/registrasi <em>online</em> melalui menu Pendaftaran Narasumber Komunitas Belajar pada halaman Beranda Aspro SDMA;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l6 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 54.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Peserta mengisi Formulir Pendaftaran secara lengkap sesuai dengan minat, kualifikasi, dan kompetensi Peserta;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l6 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 54.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Peserta Mengunggah Daftar riwayat hidup/CV terbaru;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l6 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 54.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Pendaftaran dibuka sepanjang waktu;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l6 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 54.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">5.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none; mso-fareast-language: EN-ID;\">Peserta yang akan diundang akan terlebih dahulu mengikuti pertemuan teknis dengan Tim Pengurus Aspro SDMA.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l6 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 54.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -35.45pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo4; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 35.45pt;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-ID\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-font-kerning: 0